# Requests del caso de uso ResolveEvent (tRPC MUTATION). Resuelve un evento abierto.
# Requiere la extensión "REST Client" (humao.rest-client): clic en "Send Request".
# Levantá la API y corré el seed antes:  pnpm exec nx serve @org/api  /  pnpm seed
# Tomá un @eventId real con event.history?input={"status":"abierto"}.

@host = http://localhost:3001
@eventId = pegar-un-id-abierto-del-history

### ✅ Resolver con nota (la nota solo se deja al resolver) → 200 + DTO status="resuelto"
POST {{host}}/trpc/event.resolve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "{{eventId}}",
  "note": "Incidente atendido por la guardia"
}

### ✅ Resolver sin nota → 200 (resolutionNote queda null)
POST {{host}}/trpc/event.resolve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "{{eventId}}"
}

### ❌ Resolver uno ya resuelto → 409 CONFLICT (alreadyResolved)
POST {{host}}/trpc/event.resolve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "{{eventId}}"
}

### ❌ eventId inexistente → 404 NOT_FOUND
POST {{host}}/trpc/event.resolve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "99999999-9999-4999-8999-999999999999"
}

### ❌ eventId vacío → 400 (lo frena Zod: min(1))
POST {{host}}/trpc/event.resolve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": ""
}
